                         rat game 16
rat game is a passion project by two idiots and we're on the
sixteenth version of it. it's currently a game built to run on
someone's server (yes i mean you plug in a screen to the
server rack and that's what you play it on) because that's
hilarious and also stupid and also means i don't have to care
about shading languages though it might be easy to use openacc
or cuda idk anything actually
                       things we've done
- you can load & texture models from files then walk around
  them
- menus are implemented
- with custom fonts
- the whole 3d thing is a little bit good maybe (shading,
  depth, textures, clipping (still need to do frustum culling
  though))
